  "message": "docs(malloc): add bounds_audit_fixture.json enumerating proven bounds checks\n\nRecords the static/dynamic bounds-check audit for allocator-internal index\nsites in crates/frankenlibc-core/src/malloc/. All 7 bounds checks in\nThreadCache (alloc, dealloc, drain_magazine, is_full) and MallocState\n(central_bin pop/push/len paths inside malloc/free) are statically proven\nwith zero remaining dynamic checks, matching the auditing approach used\nfor other safety-critical paths in the allocator.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
